branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
Series MGPA is a compact body actuator integrated with internal guide shafts to isolate the load bearing from the movement of the actuator&apos;s rod and seals. The press fitted high precision ball bushing results in a non-rotating accuracy of +/-0.01&#xb0; across all bore sizes.
&lt;/p&gt;

branchItem.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The MGPA is a compact body actuator integrated with internal guide shafts to isolate the load bearing from the movement of the actuator&apos;s rod and seals. The press fitted high precision ball bushing results in a non-rotating accuracy of +/-0.01&#xb0; across all bore sizes. The stroke adjustment option (XC8, XC9) can be either on the extend or retract cycle and has an adjustment range up to 50 mm.
&lt;/p&gt;

branchItem.bullets:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bore sizes: 12, 16, 20, 25, 32, 40, 50, 63, 80, 100 mm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Non-rotating accuracy of +/-0.01&amp;deg; across all bore sizes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adjustable stroke option, extent cycle (XC8)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adjustable stroke option, retract cycle (XC9)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Rubber bumpers as standard&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Auto switch capable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

