&lt;p&gt;
The MGPAF-Z is a compact body actuator integrated with internal guide shafts to isolate the load bearing from the movement of the actuator&apos;s rod and seals. The press fitted high precision ball bushing results in a non-rotating accuracy of +/-0.01&#xb0; across all bore sizes. It is available with a plate side flange.
&lt;/p&gt;

